wikipedia_page.main: Sonny Webster (born 10 March 1994) is a British  weightlifter. He placed 14th at the 2016 Summer Olympics totaling 333kg. He is also the founder of the athletic sportswear brand Big Friday Supplies, and the head coach of The Lifting Zone (previously The Sonny Webster Academy).

response: First-time Olympians Sonny Webster and Rebekah Tiler were named to Team GB's weightlifting team for the Games on 29 June 2016.
